title: I transfered my account from EUW to NA
body: I have several accounts when I transfered this account BACK to NA I have apparently 2 accounts with the same user name but the passwords where different but it will not let me log on to the account I need help PLEASE.

replies.body: It sounds like you're not having this problem with *this* account but actually a different one? What's the summoner name of the account you're having issues with, and which region is it currently on?
